-- Create and load AirPollution table
CREATE TABLE AirPollution (
    lon FLOAT,
    lat FLOAT,
    aqi INT,
    co FLOAT,
    no FLOAT,
    no2 FLOAT,
    o3 FLOAT,
    so2 FLOAT,
    pm2_5 FLOAT,
    pm10 FLOAT,
    nh3 FLOAT,
    corrected_timestamp INT,
    location NVARCHAR(100),
    date_time DATETIME2,
    id NVARCHAR(100),
    o3_8hr FLOAT,
    o3_1hr FLOAT,
    pm2_5_24hr FLOAT,
    pm10_24hr FLOAT,
    co_8hr FLOAT,
    so2_1hr FLOAT,
    so2_24hr FLOAT,
    no2_1hr FLOAT,
    us_aqi INT
);
GO

INSERT INTO AirPollution (
    lon,
    lat,
    aqi,
    co,
    no,
    no2,
    o3,
    so2,
    pm2_5,
    pm10,
    nh3,
    corrected_timestamp,
    location,
    date_time,
    id,
    o3_8hr,
    o3_1hr,
    pm2_5_24hr,
    pm10_24hr,
    co_8hr,
    so2_1hr,
    so2_24hr,
    no2_1hr,
    us_aqi
)
SELECT
    lon,
    lat,
    aqi,
    co,
    no,
    no2,
    o3,
    so2,
    pm2_5,
    pm10,
    nh3,
    corrected_timestamp,
    location,
    date_time,
    id,
    o3_8hr,
    o3_1hr,
    pm2_5_24hr,
    pm10_24hr,
    co_8hr,
    so2_1hr,
    so2_24hr,
    no2_1hr,
    us_aqi
FROM
    ExternalAirPollution;
